title: PRIVATE TWINHOME WITH A LARGE FULLY FENCED YARD
posting_body: ['Split Entry TwinHome in wonderful Blaine', '3 Bedrooms - 1 Bedroom Upper Level, 2 Bedrooms Lower Level', '2 Baths - Full Bath Upper Level, 3/4 Lower Level', 'Newer Hardwood Floors on Upper and Lower Level', 'Updated Light Fixtures', 'Recently Installed Garage Door and Door Opener', 'Several Years Old High Efficiency Windows Throughout the Property', 'Newer 4-Panel Wood Interior Doors', 'Walkout Upper Level to the Deck', 'Oversized Attached 2 Car Garage', 'Central A/C', 'All Appliances Included - Microwave Washer Dryer Dishwasher Stove Refrigerator', 'Large, Fully Fenced Private Yard, Great for Family with Kids and/or Pets.', 'Located on Quiet Residential Street', 'Monthly Rent - $1800', 'Tenants Pay All Utilities', 'Security Deposit - $1800', 'First Month Rent, Last Month Rent and Damage Deposit are due at the time of signing the Lease Agreement.', 'Property will be available NOVEMBER 1st, 2022.', 'Some Pets are accepted with additional rent and fee.', 'Dogs Must be 20 Pounds or Less.', 'Cats Must be Neutered or Spayed.', 'No Puppies or Kittens Please.', 'Tenants are responsible for lawn care and snow removal.', 'This Property is not Section 8 Certified.', 'GOOD RENTAL HISTORY IS ESSENTIAL.', 'PLEASE PROVIDE YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION when Responding to this Post.', 'Please note, this Advertisement will be Removed as soon as Property will be Rented.', 'IF THIS AD IS UP, THE PROPERTY IS STILL AVAILABLE.', 'Surrounding Cities: Anoka, Andover, Ham Lake, Fridley, Coon Rapids, Circle Pines, Champlin, Brooklyn Park, Dayton, Spring Lake Park, Mounds View, Arden Hills, Lino Lakes, Centerville, Shoreview, Columbus']
